k><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zeH40lG.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Link to original tweet https://twitter.com/GBBranstetter/status/1519395789910462466</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rz7jB9Z.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Link to the Trevor Project, which saves LGBT+ lives on the daily https://www.thetrevorproject.org/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zGD8P5i.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Link to article https://www.advocate.com/news/2022/3/28/police-19-year-old-trans-woman-kathryn-newhouse-killed-father</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XDB1NZp.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Link to article https://www.nbcnews.com/feature/nbc-out/mom-pleads-guilty-murder-8-year-old-boy-thought-be-n848741</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FPm3uiM.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Link to article https://www.nbcnews.com/feature/nbc-out/nevada-father-murdered-son-being-gay-former-foster-mom-claims-n817906

Just felt it might be good to spread a bit of truth about the horrors of anti-LGBT violence that bigots will do against even their own children, given the rhetoric these same people have about protecting kids. Maybe show one of these next time someone wants to whine about the 'leftist agenda' to 'brainwash kids'.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WS5lq16</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Altanese]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Interspecies trading with birds</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HoAFX2M</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sYyCnuS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"What do you do for a living?"
"Oh I trade nuts for money with crows"

Trading has been documented from every known human society and it's been done for a very long time. Seems even some birds can do it, crows are some of the most intelligent species on the planet.

Now who would teach crows some socially sustainable distribution of nuts?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HoAFX2M</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[insanitycontinuum]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What a cute Tigow</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7zjF8es</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RblUmpQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/7zjF8es</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[5ywjdPumpkinPrincess]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Very interesting </title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/hi6IBOt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0TL8JZD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bRXQbVn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/hi6IBOt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheRainbowegoSweet007]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9U7wLDM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dyhOYIv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9U7wLDM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Noonius]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hehe</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/f6XOhPs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AXHPEo6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/33NZi6p.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fn7okRd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The Brits did vote for this.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/f6XOhPs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Waaaazzzzzuuuuuupppppp]]></dc:creator